{"tid":243981,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇物理高手話我知點解會甩鞋帶？","createTime":"2017-05-15T05:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T01:42:20.000Z","uid":76399,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa9c423ad2a5bab8ba431d0d85e9757b6bf05c3e","tid":243981,"uid":76399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:18:54.000Z","msg":"明明縛到好撚實，打哂結。<br />\n點解行路會令到條鞋帶鬆左？ 唔係應該有磨擦力令到佢地唔會甩出嚟架咩？<br />\n我睇唔透呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5859a8ad4d54fcd800c3b1c4f38bfa3a10ccd7","tid":243981,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:19:32.000Z","msg":"磁量通"},{"pid":"4670a8601d2082208e87d2bf7c5dc189915034c7","tid":243981,"uid":15251,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"行路導致鞋帶磁通量密度嘅改變"},{"pid":"75d541424dff077ed52a0bfc2fa84c6c09385096","tid":243981,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>磁量通</blockquote><br />\n你對鞋有磁石架？"},{"pid":"b46b791619c964d77928c1704fb87f39335e8238","tid":243981,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行路導致鞋帶磁通量密度嘅改變</blockquote><br />\n咁關甩鞋帶咩事"},{"pid":"483d663dacf35886fa5a2fb716a11f45cd3f0168","tid":243981,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2f267de683f852b17c4ce93a3ebaa15c0d55a5","tid":243981,"uid":54066,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:29:51.000Z","msg":"「我們看上去有些瘋狂，因為當我們在伯克利的大廳中走路時也會盯着鞋帶自動解開。」該團隊成員、酷愛跑步的Christine Gregg說。她在一台跑步機上跑步，讓同事以慢動作錄製她的鞋子以捕捉鞋帶解開的細節。<br />\n<br />\n他們發現罪魁禍首是跑步時生成的慣力集合。一個結通常是通過中心的摩擦力在維繫。這正是更結實的結匝數更多的原因，每個匝都會產生摩擦力。<br />\n<br />\n但跑步時不斷向下踩腳則會在結的底部形成加速度，每跑一步鞋帶會前後甩動，像一隻無形的手一樣在末端牽引。最終，當加速度超過內部摩擦力時這個結就會到達臨界點，然後立刻自動解開。"},{"pid":"cf9460e2a96f2e8a6ff108ce22b4c9f22c00b7dc","tid":243981,"uid":83305,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767eac44d47119b4a49249340ae69513a9fc88ea","tid":243981,"uid":102763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8886802746b63d0dd5cfa82ef4c756b94fa86b","tid":243981,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T06:17:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「我們看上去有些瘋狂，因為當我們在伯克利的大廳中走路時也會盯着鞋帶自動解開。」該團隊成員、酷愛跑步的Christine Gregg說。她在一台跑步機上跑步，讓同事以慢動作錄製她的鞋子以捕捉鞋帶解開的細節。<br />\n<br />\n他們發現罪魁禍首是跑步時生成的慣力集合。一個結通常是通過中心的摩擦力在維繫。這正是更結實的結匝數更多的原因，每個匝都會產生摩擦力。<br />\n<br />\n但跑步時不斷向下踩腳則會在結的底部形成加速度，每跑一步鞋帶會前後甩動，像一隻無形的手一樣在末端牽引。最終，當加速度超過內部摩擦力時這個結就會到達臨界點，然後立刻自動解開。</blockquote><br />\n屌，原來真係有人做過Research<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d459db28120ede337a1b66f15cf8869457463b","tid":243981,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T06:21:12.000Z","msg":"綑多個結就得"},{"pid":"41df6760f9728959f37557f9201f47b55b9415d7","tid":243981,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T06:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>綑多個結就得</blockquote><br />\n我係想知點解單結會甩出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13edbf6ccef4a97ee048b438f7218091f9934f8b","tid":243981,"uid":41742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T06:37:48.000Z","msg":"搭單問， 點解堆電腦線會識自己打結"},{"pid":"b3952740c6204f632f87a7d77172420b0ba1fc85","tid":243981,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-1